content: That's really helpful. I think I'll also add a column to track the shipping method and delivery time, so I can see which websites are the fastest and most reliable. And maybe a column for the product category, so I can see where I'm spending the most money. Do you have any suggestions on how to stay organized with my online shopping apps on my phone? I've got a bunch of shopping apps on my phone, and it's getting hard to keep track of which ones I've logged into and which ones I haven't.
